author: Fextralife
description:
ASKA Gameplay Preview - SHOULD You PLAY It? Is It Worth it? (Survival Colony Sim)
In this video, we're going to be taking a look at Aska, a new mythical co-op survival and colony simulation game that launched into early access on Steam in July of last year. Aska gameplay focuses on base building, surviving destructive seasons, earning the gods' favor, and fighting ancient terrors.

Get the game here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1898300/ASKA/
Sponsored by:  Sand Sailor Studio
